Project libraries live here.

Canonical core stack:
- `AudioProcessor`: microphone capture, cleaning, and FFT helpers.
- `Logic`: alert-state policy and finite-state-machine behavior.
- `DisplayManager`: round TFT rendering and UI helpers.

Rule of thumb:
- Add core detection logic to `AudioProcessor` or `Logic`.
- Add local UI output to `DisplayManager`.
- Build future integrations on top of the working on-device pipeline instead of in parallel with it.
